    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows minor road rash and interior bolsters exhibit light patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with updated polyurethane bushings for improved turn-in precision.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Runs well with no major issues.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking both luxury and reliability. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant luster, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and well-preserved, free from any cracks or unsightly wear. All onboard electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has clearly been a point of pride for its previous owner. It comes complete with two sets of keys, a full service log, and the original owner\u2019s manuals, ready for its next chapter on the road.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and refined performance. This unit has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a driving experience that balances reliability with sophisticated engineering. Every component has been evaluated to meet our standards of excellence, offering the discerning buyer an exceptional value proposition. We invite you to experience the quality and poise of this well-preserved automobile.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, ready to hit the road for many more miles! It runs beautifully and has been well-loved, making it a perfect pick if you want something dependable and comfortable without the 'brand new' price tag. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six features a 11.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, delivering peak power at 7,900 RPM. The double VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing across the rev range. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior power delivery. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with a well-maintained driver, the mechanical components remain robust, providing a tactile and precise driving experience.",
